verses.text: Mamin Jehová, te wach' yic eb' sk'anab'ajan a k'ayb'ub'al, malaj mach tz'alan eb' chucal.
Te wach' yic eb' sk'anab'ajan a cachnab'il, t'a smasanil sk'ol eb' tz'och tzak'an uuj.
Aton eb' max k'ulanlaj chucal, eb' sk'anab'ajan sb'eyb'alan tas tzala'.
Mamin Jehová, a ach ix ala' to tz'acan tz'aj sk'anab'ajax a checnab'il.
Comonoc aynhejoch t'a in k'ool in k'anab'ajan a ley.
¿Tas yuj ol in q'uixvoc tato tzin k'anab'ajej masanil a checnab'il chi'?
Ol val wach' lolonel t'ayach t'a smasanil in k'ool ayic toxo ix in k'ayb'ej a ley te tojol.
Ol in k'anab'ajej a ley. Manh in actejcan t'a junelnhej. BET
¿Tas val ol aj eb' quelemtac yic max och smul eb'? Anhej tato sk'anab'ajej a lolonel eb'.
D'a smasanil in k'ol tzin och tzak'an uuj. Manh a cha viq'uel in b'ha t'a a checnab'il.
Ix cham val in k'ayb'an a lolonel yic wach' max och in mul t'ayach.
Mamin Jehová, te wach' ach. k'ayb'ej in t'a a ley.
Ol valel masanil a ley, aton juntzanh alb'ilcan uuj.
Ek'b'al stzalaj in k'ool ayic tzin k'anab'ajan in cachnab'il tzak'a' t'a yichanh pax svik'an masanil macanhil b'eyumal.
Ol in naub'tanhej a checnab'il ix ak' t'ayonh. Ol cham val in naub'tanhan a k'ayb'ub'al.
Ol vak' tzalajb'oc in k'ool yet' a checnab'il tik, manh ol b'atcan a lolonel satk'olal vuuj. GUÍMEL
Ak' a wach'k'olal t'ayin yic wach' ol in k'anab'ajej a lolonel yacb'an pitzan into.
Jac in sat yic wach' snachajel a k'ayb'ub'al vuuj, aton te satub'tac yochi.
Eq'uelb'anhej vek' t'a sat lu'um tik, manh a k'ub'ejel a checnab'il t'ayin.
Snib'ej val in k'ol svojtaquejel a ley t'a junjun rato.
Ha ach ton tza cach eb' ak'umtac syutej sb'a, aton eb' catab'il yujto syiq'uel sb'a eb' t'a a checnab'il.
Yujto tzin k'anab'ajej in cachnab'il tzak'a', yuj chi' colinel t'a schucal lolonel eb' tzin paticaneli.
Wach'chom a eb' yajal smol naej eb' in yixtani, a inxo a checab' in tik, a a ley ol in naub'tanhej.
Svak' tzalaj in k'ool yuj in cachnab'il, yujto syak' in razón. DÁLET
Ijan val tzin cham svab'i, ak' in q'uinal ichataxon alani.
Ix in ch'ox chajtil in b'ey t'a ichanh, ix in a tak'vani. k'ayb'ej in t'a a b'eyb'al.
Ak' nachajel vuuj yic wach' tzin k'anab'ajej a checnab'il. In gana tzin naub'tanhej juntzanh tas ix a k'ulej to satub'tac yochi.
Ay in och t'a cusk'olal, tek'an tzin utej in k'ana' icha yaj alancani.
Ochanh ved'oc yic wach' max vesej, tzak'an a wach'k'olal t'ayin yuj a k'ayb'ub'al.
Toxo ix vak'och t'a in k'ool to yelnhej tas ol vala', tzin nib'ej a ley.
Mamin Jehová, te naan in cachnab'il ix ak'a', manh in a cha q'uixvoc.
Van vak'an vip in k'anab'ajan a checnab'il yujto van ak'an in pensar. HE
Mamin Jehová, k'ayb'ej in t'a a ley, in gana tzin k'anab'ajej masanto t'a slajvub'.
Ak' nachajel vuuj yic wach' ol in k'anab'ajej a k'ayb'ub'al. D'a val smasanil in k'ool in gana tzin k'anab'ajej a k'ayb'ub'al chi'.
Cuchb'ej in t'a sb'eal a checnab'il, yujto ay in tzalajk'olal t'ay.
Ak' in nib'ejoch in cachnab'il tzak'a, mocab' b'eyumal tzin nib'ejochi.
Manh a cha vak'och in pensar t'a juntzanh yechel comon dios. Ak' in q'uinal, yic wach' svak'och a k'ayb'ub'al t'a in k'ool.
Hak'uelk'och t'ayin a in a checab' in tik, juntzanh tas alb'ilcan uuj t'a eb' ay elk'och t'a yol sat.
Te wach' a ley t'a yol in sat, yuj chi' colinel t'a juntzanh lolonel stzuntzancot yoval in k'ool, to tzin xiv t'ay.
Te xajanab'il a checnab'il vuuj, ak' in q'uinal, yujto tojol ach toni. VAW
Mamin Jehová, ak' a wach'k'olal yet' a colval t'ayin, ichataxon alani.
Icha chi' ol yal in pactzitan eb' tzin tzuntzani, yujto a a lolonel ayoch yipoc in k'ool.
Ochanh ved'oc yic svalel a lolonel te yel, yujto yipk'olal yaj a ley vuuj.
In gana tzin k'anab'ajej a k'ayb'ub'al, malajocab' b'ak'uinh svactejcani.
Junk'olal ol in ajoc, yujto svak'och a ley t'a in k'ool.
Ha t'a yichanh eb' vinh rey ol valel a checnab'il, manh ol in q'uixvoclaj valani.
Te xajan a checnab'il vuuj, ay pax in tzalajk'olal yuj.
Tzin xajanej val a checnab'il, in gana val yaji. Tzin te naub'tanhej a ley chi'. ZAÍN
Nacot tas alnaccan t'ayin, a in a checab' in tik, a a lolonel chi' ix vak'och yipoc in k'ool.
Ha lolonel chi' tz'ak'an snivanil in k'ool ayic ilk'olal vaji. Ha tas alnaccan chi', aton van yak'an in q'uinal.
Ha eb' te ak'umtac, max yactej eb' in stzuntzani, palta max vactejcanlaj a k'ayb'ub'al.
Mamin Jehová, tzin nacot juntzanh a ley aytax ek' t'a yichb’anel. Ha t'a juntzanh chi' svik' snivanil in k'ool.
Ha eb' sk'ulan chucal, syactejcan a k'ayb'ub'al eb', yuj chi' ste cot voval.
Ha a ley ix vak'och in b'itoc t'a sat lu'um tik, yujto eq'uelb'anhej veq'ui.
Mamin Jehová, tzach in nacot t'ak'walil, in gana tzin k'anab'ajejnhej a k'ayb'ub'al.
Sja in tzalajk'olal yujto tzin k'anab'ajej a checnab'il chi'. CHET
Mamin Jehová, a achnhej tzach in nib'ej. Toxo ix vak' in ti' to tzin k'anab'ajej tas tzala'.
D'a val smasanil in k'ool tzin na'a to svak' tzalajb'oc a k'ool. Ok'oc a k'ool t'ayin, ichataxon alancani.
Ix in b'eytzitej in b'eyb'al, ix in yamoch in k'anab'ajan in cachnab'il tzak'a'.
D'a elanhchamel svak' vip in k'anab'ajan a checnab'il.
Ha eb' sk'ulan chucal ix yaq'uem yaal eb' t'a vichanh, palta max b'atlaj a k'ayb'ub'al satk'olal vuuj.
Ha t'a chimilak'val tzin q'ue vaan svak'an yuj diosal t'ayach yuj a ley, yujto tojol toni.
Wach' vak'an yet' eb' syaq'uem sb'a t'ayach yet' eb' sk'anab'ajan a checnab'il.
Mamin Jehová, niwan chequel a wach'k'olal t'a yol yib'anhk’inal tik, k'ayb'ej in t'a a ley. TET
Mamin Jehová, wach' ton ix utej a k'ool t'ayin a in a checab' in tik, ichataxon alancani.
In gana tzin a k'ayb'ej t'a a jelanil yet' t'a tas scojtaquej, yujto a a checnab'il svak'och yipoc in k'ool.
Ayic manto och in yaelal, manh jantacoc b'aj ix in b'at t'a skal chucal, haxo ticnaic jun, tzin k'anab'ajej a lolonel.
Ha ach tik, te wach' ach, wach'nhej tas tza k'ulej. k'ayb'ej in t'a a b'eyb'al.
Ha eb' ak'umtac, syal lolonel eb' manh yeloc t'a in patic, a inxo jun, tzin k'anab'ajej a checnab'il t'a smasanil in k'ool.
Ix ixtaxel spensar eb' sk'ulan chucal, xal in jun, svak' tzalajb'oc in k'ool t'a a k'ayb'ub'al.
Te wach' ix in elk'ochi yujto ix och in yaelal. Ichaton val chi' ix aj in k'ayb'an a b'eyb'al.
Ha a k'ayb'ub'al t'ayin ek'b'al yelk'och t'a yichanh q'uen tzijtumal oro yet' q'uen plata. YOD
Ha ach ton val ix in a b'o'o. Ak' in jelanil yic wach' tzin k'ayb'ej a checnab'il.
Ha eb' ay elk'och t'a yol sat, tzalajocab' sk'ool eb' ayic tzin yilan eb' yujto a a lolonel ix vak'och yipoc in k'ool.
Mamin Jehová, vojtac to te tojol a ley. Ayic tzin ak'anoch t'a ilk'olal, ayton val yuj, yuj chi' icha chi' tzutej.
Aocab' a wach'k'olal snivanan in k'ool ichataxon alan t'ayin.
Ch'ox svach'il a k'ool t'ayin, tzak'an pax in q'uinal. Ay val in tzalajk'olal yuj a k'ayb'ub'al.
Q'uixvocab'el eb' ak'umtac syutej sb'a, yujto tzin sb'aj eb' wach'chom malaj in mul t'a eb'. Ha inxo tik tzin naub'tanhej a checnab'il.
Ha eb' ay elk'och t'a sat, eb' ojtannac cachnab'il tzak'a', smolb'ejocab' sb'a eb' ved'oc.
Wach'ocab'nhej yaj in pensar icha syal a ley, yic wach' malaj b'aj ol in q'uixvoc. CAF
Toxonhej nanon yek' in k'ool b'ak'uinh ol in a colo', palta a a lolonel svak'och yipoc in k'ool.
Van yixtax yol in sat yuj in maclani b'ak'uinh ol elk'och tas alnaccani. Tzin naan icha tik: ¿B'aq'uinh ol ach ja ak' snivanil in k'ool? xin chi.
Wach'chom manhxalaj vopisio yujto icham inxo, palta max b'atlaj a ley satk'olal vuuj.
¿Jantacto tiempo ol vil a in a checab' in tik? ¿B'aq'uinhto val ol ak'och syaelal eb' ayoch ajk'olal t'ayin?
Ha eb' ak'umtac syutej sb'a, manh naanoc a k'ayb'ub'al yuj eb'. Toxo ix sjoy olan eb' yic tzin telvi t'ay yalan eb'.
Masanil a checnab'il, yelnhej syala'. Ochanh ved'oc, ina to malaj in mul, palta manh jantacoc eb' ayoch ajk'olal t'ayin.
Toxo ijan tzin cham yuj eb', palta max b'atlaj a checnab'il satk'olal vuuj.
Ak' in q'uinal, icha syal jantac a wach'k'olal, icha chi' ol in k'anab'ajej in cachnab'il ix ak'a'. LAMED
Mamin Jehová, a a lolonel max q'uexmajlaj. Aynhejek' t'a masanil q'uinal t'a satcha’anh.
Ha ach tik, tz'elnhejk'och tas tzal t'a masanil tiempo. Ha ach a b'onac lum lum tik, yuj chi' anheja' yaj lu'um ticnaic.
Masanil tasi, anheja' yaji ichataxon yaj alannaccani, anhejtona' ha' van a k'anan ticnaic.
Tato maj in tzalaj in naub'tanhan a k'ayb'ub'al, toxom ix in lajviel yuj cusk'olal.
Malaj b'ak'uinh sb'atcan a checnab'il satk'olal vuuj. Ha yuj a lolonel tik ix ak' in q'uinal.
Colin yujto ic innhej toni, naannhej a checnab'il vuuj.
Ha eb' sk'ulan chucal, van stanhvan eb' in lajvieli, palta a inxo jun, a val a cachnab'il tzala', a tzin naub'tanhej.
Ix wila'' to malaj junok tas tz'ak'an wach'il, haxo a checnab'il, manhxo jantacoc svach'il. MEM
Te xajan a k'ayb'ub'al vuuj. Masanil tiempo tzin naub'tanhej.
Naannhej a checnab'il vuuj, yuj chi' yelxo val jelan in t'a yichanh eb' ayoch ajk'olal t'ayin.
Ek'al in jelanil t'a yichanh masanil eb' in k'ayb'umal, yujto naannhej a k'ayb'ub'al vuuj.
Yelxo val snachajel vuuj t'a yichanh eb' ichamtac vinac, yujto tzin k'anab'ajej a checnab'il.
Max yal-laj in k'ol svak'och in b'ha t'a chuc b'eyb'al, yic wach' tzin k'anab'ajejnhej a lolonel.
Maj viq'uel-laj in b'ha t'a a k'ayb'ub'al, yujto van in a k'ayb'ani.
Ek'b'al schi'al a lolonel t'a yichanh schi'al nok' yal chab' svab'i.
Te ay in jelanil ix viq'uelta t'a a checnab'il, yuj chi' tzin chaquel masanil chuc b'eyb'al. NUN
Ha a lolonel sch'oxan wach' b'eyb'al t'ayin ichato a tz'ak'an sakil k'inal t'a yol in b'e, ha' sch'oxan b'e t'ayin.
Ach in Diosal, ix vak' in ti' t'ayach, yuj chi' yovalil ol in k'anab'ajej. Ol in k'ayb'ej in b'ha t'a a ley to te tojol.
Mamin Jehová, yelxo val ste cus in k'ool svab'i. Ak' in q'uinal ichataxon alani.
Mamin, cha in wach' lolonel sval t'ayach t'a smasanil in k'ool, tzin a k'ayb'an pax t'a a k'ayb'ub'al.
Junjun k'u sjavi tas ay smay t'a vib'anh, palta max b'atcanlaj a k'ayb'ub'al satk'olal vuuj.
Ha eb' sk'ulan chucal, syaq'uem in yaalil eb', palta max b'atlaj a checnab'il satk'olal vuuj.
Ha a lolonel ix al t'ayin, vicnhej yaj t'a masanil tiempo, yujto ha' tz'ak'an in tzalajk'olal.
Toxo ix vak' pensar to ol in k'anab'ajej a ley masanto t'a slajvub'. SAMEC
Tzin chaquel eb' anima chab' sat, palta tzin xajanej a k'ayb'ub'al.
Ha ach ton ay ach och venhuloc yet' in colnab'iloc. Ha a lolonel ayoch yipoc in k'ool.
Elanhec t'a in tz'ey a ex tze k'ulej chucal, yujto in gana tzin k'anab'ajej schecnab'il in Diosal.
Mamin, ak' vip, ichataxon yaj alancani, yic aynhej in q'uinal. Manh ak' lajvoc tas ayoch yipoc in k'ool.
Ochanh ved'oc, yic ol in colchajoc. Ichato chi' ol in k'anab'ajan a ley.
Ix a tek'canem eb' syiq'uel sb'ha t'a a ley, yujto a sjelanil eb' malaj yelk'ochi.
Icha val k'alem, icha chi' yaj eb' sk'ulan chucal t'a yol a sat, yuj chi' tzin xajanej a lolonel.
Ha in nivanil tik, tz'ib'xi yuj in xivk'olal t'ayach, yujto te niwan yelk'och a ley t'ayin. 'AYIN
Ha wach'il yet' tojolal tzin b'eyb'alej. Manh in actejcan t'a yol sk'ab' eb' ayoch ajk'olal t'ayin.
Ochanh vilumaloc yuj in wach'iloc. Mocab' in yixtej eb' ak'umtac syutej sb'a.
Van yixtaxel yol in sat yuj in maclan a javi yic tzul in a colani. Van in tanhvan in ik'anel t'a libre ichataxon alancani.
Wach' tzutej a k'ol t'ayin a in a checab' in tik, icha jantac a wach'k'olal. k'ayb'ej in t'a a ley.
Ak' in jelanil a in a checab' in tik. In gana svojtaquejel a cachnab'il tzala'.
Mamin Jehová, stiempoalxo ak'an syaelal eb' sk'ulan chucal, yujto ix spitej sb'a eb' t'a a k'ayb'ub'al.
Ek'b'al tzin nib'ej a checnab'il t'a yichanh q'uen oro te wach',
yuj chi' tzin k'anab'ajejnhej a checnab'il chi', haxo pax masanil chuc b'eyb'al, tzin chaccaneli. PE
Satub'tac a cachnab'il, yuj val chi' tzin k'anab'ajej t'ay.
Ayic tz'alchajel tas syalelk'och a lolonel, icha val sakil k'inal yaj t'ayonh. Sk'ayb'aj eb' anima emnaquil yuj.
Tzin te nib'ej val a checnab'il, icha val snib'an ha ha' junok mach yuj taquinhtial.
Ilincoti, ok'oc val a k'ol t'ayin icha val tzutej a k'ol t'a eb' tzach xajanani.
Cuchb'ej in t'a a b'eyb'al, icha val yalan a lolonel. Manh in a cha ak'joc ganar yuj chucal.
Colinel t'a eb' anima malaj yoq'uelk'olal. In gana tzin k'anab'ajej a checnab'il.
Tzalajocab' a k'ool vuj a in a checab' in tik, tzin a k'ayb'anpax t'a a ley.
Tzin te oq'ui, yujto malaj yelk'och a k'ayb'ub'al t'a eb' vetanimail. TZADE
Mamin Jehová, tojol ach toni, wach'nhej yelk'och a ley.
Masanil a cachnab'il, tojol toni, yuj chi' syal cak'anoch t'a co k'ool.
Te tacnac in k'ool yuj eb' ayoch ajk'olal t'ayin, yujto ix b'atcan a lolonel satk'olal yuj eb'.
Ha tas tzala' tz'elnhejk'ochi, yuj chi' tzin xajanej a in a checab' in tik.
Emnaquil anima in, paticab'il in el yuj eb' vetanimail, palta max b'atcanlaj a checnab'il satk'olal vuuj.
Ha a tojolal malaj b'ak'uinh slajvi. Ha a k'ayb'ub'al yelnhej syala'.
Manhxo animaoc vaj yuj cusk'olal yet' yaelal, haxo a checnab'il tz'ak'an in tzalajk'olal.
Ha a cachnab'il tojolnhej toni. Ak' ja in pensar yic wach' aynhej in q'uinal. COF
Mamin Jehová, t'a val smasanil in k'ool tzin avaj t'ayach, tak'vej in, yujto in gana tzin k'anab'ajej a ley.
Ha t'ayach sval in b'a. Ochanh ved'oc yic wach' ol in k'anab'ajej a cachnab'il tzala'.
Ayic manto sacb'ilaj tzin q'ue vaan, tzin k'anan a colval yujto svak'och a lolonel yipoc in k'ool.
Pitzan in tzek' ak'val, tzin naub'tanhan tas alb'ilcan uuj.
Mamin Jehová, ab' tas svala' icha jantac a wach'k'olal. Ak' in q'uinal icha val stojolal a b'eyb'al.
Ha eb' snaan yak'an chucal t'ayin, ayek' eb' t'a in lak'anil, palta najat yajcan eb' t'a a k'ayb'ub'al.
Ha achxo pax Mamin, te lak'an ayach eq'ui, yelton val syal masanil a checnab'il.
Pecatax ix vojtaquejel yuj a cachnab'il tik, a ach ix ak'kan t'a junelnhej. REX
Mamin, ilincot yet' in yaelal tik, tzin a colani yujto max b'atcan a k'ayb'ub'al satk'olal vuuj.
Colinel t'a yol sk'ab' eb' tz'esanoch t'a vib'anh. Ak' in q'uinal ichataxon alani.
Ha eb' sk'ulan chucal, malaj yalan yic eb' t'a a colval, yujto max sk'anab'ajejlaj a checnab'il eb'.
Mamin Jehová, te niwan tz'ok' a k'ool t'ayonh. Ak' in q'uinal icha val a tojolal.
Manh jantacoc eb' ayoch ajk'olal t'ayin yet' eb' tzin ixtani, a inxo jun, max viq'uel-laj in b'ha t'a a cachnab'il.
Tzin chaquel eb' tzek' yib'anh sk'ulan chucal, aton eb' max k'anab'ajan a lolonel.
Mamin Jehová, yelxo val xajan a checnab'il vuuj. Ak' in q'uinal icha val jantac a wach'k'olal.
Ha a lolonel te yel. Tojolton masanil a k'ayb'ub'al, malaj b'ak'uinh ol lajvoqueloc. SIN
Wach'chom malaj in mul, tzin spech b'eyek' eb' anima niwan yopisio, palta te niwan yelk'och a lolonel t'ayin.
Stzalaj in k'ool yuj tas alnaccani, icha junok mach te niwan sb'eyumal syik'a'.
Max yal-laj in k'ool naojq'ue lolonel, ste taccanel in k'ool yuj, palta tzin xajanej a k'ayb'ub'al.
D'a junjun rato svalan wach' lolonel t'ayach, yujto tojol ton a ley.
Ha eb' xajanan a k'ayb'ub'al, junk'olalnhej yaj eb', malaj tas tz'ak'an telvoc eb'.
Mamin Jehová, van in tanhvan in a colani, yujto van in k'anab'ajan a checnab'il.
Van in k'anab'ajan a cachnab'il te xajan vuuj.
Van in k'anab'ajan a checnab'il yet' a cachnab'il. Ojtac masanil in b'eyb'al. TAV
Mamin Jehová, q'ueocab'k'och vav t'a ichanh, ak' ja in pensar ichataxon yalan a lolonel.
Axo in lesal jun, q'ueocab'k'och t'a ichanh, colineli, ichataxon yaj alancani.
Sval wach' lolonel t'ayach, yujto tzin a k'ayb'ej t'a a b'eyb'al.
Ol in b'itej junok b'it yuj tas alnaccani, yujto masanil a checnab'il tojol yaji.
Aynhejocab'cot b'achan a k'ab' t'ayin yic tzin a colani, yujto tzin te nib'ej a checnab'il.
Mamin Jehová, snib'ej val in k'ool to tzin a colo'. Ay in tzalajk'olal t'a a k'ayb'ub'al.
Tzin nib'ej to pitzaninnhej, yic wach' ol in b'itan t'ayach. Aocab' a tojolal tz'och ved'oc.
Ix in satb'at icha nok' calnel sacleminac yajb'ati. Cotanh, say in ek' a in a checab' in tik, yujto max b'atlaj a checnab'il satk'olal vuuj.
